{"tid":1949010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「眾籌」打造一個新時代嘅歷史博物館","createTime":"2020-03-29T11:04:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T11:30:43.000Z","uid":345458,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e4621cc8dbfa996d96c1355fbc492c7389795889","tid":1949010,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:04:10.000Z","msg":"主要記錄香港新時代抗爭嘅過程，<br />\n由19年6月開始記錄，<br />\n直至光復香港果刻。<br />\n<br />\n我要世界各地嘅人，<br />\n嚟到香港之後，<br />\n都可以認識呢段香港民族嘅歷史，<br />\n知道呢段歷史嘅真相，<br />\n721...831...101...<br />\n<br />\n我要我哋嘅下一代，<br />\n珍惜民主嘅貴重，<br />\n分辨黑白是非。<br />\n<br />\n我要手足每一滴汗同淚，<br />\n都被歷史完整記載下來，<br />\n唔會有任何一位手足被遺棄。<br />\n<br />\n博物館大細唔係重點，<br />\n小弟亦都冇研究過相關法例，<br />\n純粹有感而發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e33edf03377f6be13b2c249a55f0d6cbe0b17a92","tid":1949010,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:04:35.000Z","msg":"FF完畢<br />\n下一位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"356afb7b3fc76160938add89e601333c2a3c4e2b","tid":1949010,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:07:14.000Z","msg":"負乜鬼皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nFF下姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"884fb48923f4026422e25036cfaebb67c463072f","tid":1949010,"uid":293921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:08:47.000Z","msg":"有無了解過香港既64紀念館?"},{"pid":"38369561000b9648d7d79c271155466ffa3da861","tid":1949010,"uid":249794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:09:33.000Z","msg":"如果真係想建構民族 就唔只得609開始嘅歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過如果有私人地方有黎搞個展覽唔知得唔得 <br />\n好似年宵之類咁"},{"pid":"df9ce4774e26134fdaa5e27bf2e5e17ad9730c91","tid":1949010,"uid":28641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote